{"word":"καταμηλόω","slug":"καταμηλόω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n54523\" key=\"katamhlo/w\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">καταμηλόω</orth>, <sense id=\"n54523.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">put in the probe</tr_>, so as to sound wounds, <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Suid.</author></bibl>, <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Phot.</author></bibl>, etc.; or to produce vomiting, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ἔμει καταμηλῶν</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0496.tlg001:62\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Phryn.Com.</author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">62</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>: metaph., <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">κημὸν κ</foreign>. <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">use</tr_> the funnel of the ballot-jar <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">as a probe</tr_>, i.e. <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">make</tr_> a peculator <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">disgorge</tr_> what he has stolen, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0019.tlg002.perseus-grc1:1150\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ar.\">Ar.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Eq.\">Eq.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1150</biblScope> </bibl> (lyr.). </sense> <sense n=\"2\" id=\"n54523.1\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">κ. τὰ ἔρια</foreign> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">plunge</tr_> them into dyestuff, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0542.tlg001:7:169\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Poll.</author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">7.169</biblScope></bibl>.</sense> </entryFree>"}]}